title: Rouzbahan Fraij
text: Rouzbahan Raed A Fraij (born 7 April 2000), known as Rouzbahan Fraij (), is a Jordanian <a href="women%27s%20association%20football">footballer</a> who plays as a <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> for local <a href="Jordan%20Women%27s%20Football%20League">Women's League</a> club <a href="Shabab%20Al-Ordon%20Club%20%28women%29">Shabab Al-Ordon</a> and the <a href="Jordan%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Jordan women's national team</a>.
